<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/222983-not-really-a-question-unless-its-don-t">Not really a question unless its, don&#39;t you just consume historical fiction when the history is as fascinating as the intrigue? To focus on the water systems of Pompeii and surrounding towns as effected by the imminent volcanic eruption is genius and I can&#39;t put this book down. Think it is a great way to add interest to an event we already know of the outcome.</a>
</div>
